{{#> layout}}
<h1>Welcome to {{courseName}}!</h1>

<p>Dear {{firstName}},</p>

<p>Congratulations! You have successfully enrolled in <strong>{{courseName}}</strong>. We're excited to have you join us on this learning journey.</p>

<h2>Course Details</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Course: {{courseName}}</li>
    <li>Instructor: {{instructorName}}</li>
    <li>Start Date: {{startDate}}</li>
    <li>Duration: {{duration}}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Next Steps</h2>
<p>Here's what you need to do to get started:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Access your course materials through our learning platform</li>
    <li>Review the course syllabus and schedule</li>
    <li>Mark important dates in your calendar</li>
    <li>Join the course discussion forum</li>
</ol>

<a href="{{courseUrl}}" class="button">Start Learning Now</a>

<h2>Need Help?</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Visit our <a href="{{helpUrl}}">Help Center</a></li>
    <li>Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The {{companyName}} Team</p>
{{/layout}}

